        <h1>Inspired by nature</h1>
        <p>Growing up in rural Canada in a time of no Internet or social media, Nigel Shaw had all the time in the world to explore, play and 
        invent. Surrounded by natural raw materials, he learned to solve problems with instinct and piecing together whatever lay at hand. 
        Over time his skills grew into an ability to find simple and elegant solutions.</p>
        <p>As he reached middle age and hereditary high blood pressure began to affect his erectile function, he was surprised
        to find so little innovation in the field of ED.</p>
        <p>So he turned his mind to the problem, invented a uniquely simple solution, and called it Senjja.</p> 
        <p>Nigel teamed up with Mike Dunleavy, a business and legal expert, and Tony Bella, a world leading urologist. Together
        they spent years refining Senjja and proving its effectiveness in clinical trials.</p>
        <p>When they realized just how well Senjja works—when they were able to help men with severe 
        ED who had lost hope to get their mojo back—that's when the dream of Senjja began to be real.</p>
        <p>Today Senjja is just getting started on an incredible journey that will, hopefully, help millions
        of men and their partner have more amazing sex, happier and healther relationships, and better lives.</p>
